8
0:00:37.408,000 --> 0:00:4,000
but as a poison, it was the best money could buy,

9
0:00:40.732,000 --> 0:00:43,000
so women flocked to her in order to murder their husbands.

10
0:00:44.525,000 --> 0:00:49,000
