11
0:00:49.785,000 --> 0:00:53,000
because poisoning a human being is a quite difficult thing.

12
0:00:53.954,000 --> 0:00:56,000
The reason is, we have sort of a built-in poison detector.

13
0:00:57.289,000 --> 0:01:,000
